<mixertitle>GAP&nbsp;3 Share Package "grim"</mixertitle>

<h3>
  GRIM: Groups of Rational and Integer Matrices
</h3>
<p>
  Share package since release 3.4, about April 1997,
  communicated by <mixer person="Akos Seress" data="name_city"/>.<br />
  This package has not been transferred to or replaced in GAP&nbsp;4,
  but some of its functionality, e. g. determining whether an integral
  matrix group is finite, is available (by a different algorithm) as a
  method for 'IsFinite' in GAP&nbsp;4.
</p>

<h3>
  Author
</h3>
<p>
  <mixer person="Robert Beals" data="name"/>.
</p>

<h3>
  Implementation
</h3>
<p>
  <b>Language:</b> GAP&nbsp;3 <br />
  <b>Operating system:</b> Any <br />
  <b>Current version:</b> 1.0 (in the 3.4.4 distribution)
</p>

<h3>
  Description
</h3>
<p>
  GRIM (Version~1.0) is  a system for testing finiteness and integrality
  of rational matrix groups.
</p>

